<path d="M0 120L60 110C120 100 240 80 360 70C480 60 600 60 720 70C840 80 960 100 1080 110C1200 120 1320 120 1380 120H1440V0H1380C1320 0 1200 0 1080 0C960 0 840 0 720 0C600 0 480 0 360 0C240 0 120 0 60 0H0V120Z" fill="#FDF9F3"></path>
</svg>
